'''How to open the DIR-600''' (see pictures): Remove the two mounting screws that are located under the rubber paddings. The top cover is secured by 4 latches on three sides. Use a flat head screw driver to open the latches to the left and right, then lift off the top cover. Be gentle with these latches as they can break very easily.
